g.text: Alice is using an internal application where public sign-ups are not allowed
Alice wants to invite her colleague Bob
Alice uses an app-specific invitation system that send an email with an invite code to Bob
Bob can then sign up for a new account with his email (either this could allow any email or just the one for the invite),
Bob's user account will only be created after the email verification is done
The invite code will only be marked as "used" when the user is created (or it can have its own expiry date)
